<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>PULSE — Interactive App Prototype</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --bg:#0A0B0D; --surface:#141618; --surface-2:#1B1E21; --hair:rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
    --text:#F3F2EE; --text-soft:#9BA1A6; --text-faint:#5C6267;
    --calm:#1D9E75; --calm-b:#5DCAA5; --calm-bg:#0E1D18;
    --tension:#185FA5; --tension-b:#6FB0EA; --tension-bg:#0E1A24;
    --strain:#BA7517; --strain-b:#F2B341; --strain-bg:#241C0E;
    --overload:#A32D2D; --overload-b:#F16E68; --overload-bg:#240F0E;
    --burnout:#534AB7; --burnout-b:#9C94EE; --burnout-bg:#18152C;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent}
  html,body{background:#020203;height:100%}
  body{
    font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif; color:var(--text);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; min-height:100vh;
    padding:40px 20px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 800px 500px at 20% 10%, rgba(93,202,165,0.08), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 800px 500px at 85% 90%, rgba(156,148,238,0.08), transparent 60%),
      #020203;
  }
  .mono{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}
  button{font-family:inherit; cursor:pointer}

  /* ================= Phone shell ================= */
  .device{
    position:relative; width:390px; height:844px; border-radius:52px;
    background:#000; padding:14px; box-shadow:0 40px 100px -20px rgba(0,0,0,0.8), 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    flex-shrink:0;
  }
  .screen-clip{
    position:relative; width:100%; height:100%; border-radius:40px; overflow:hidden; background:var(--bg);
  }
  .island{
    position:absolute; top:14px; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%);
    width:118px; height:34px; background:#000; border-radius:20px; z-index:50;
  }
  .statusbar{
    position:absolute; top:0; left:0; right:0; height:52px; display:flex; align-items:center;
    justify-content:space-between; padding:0 30px; z-index:40; color:#fff; font-size:15px; font-weight:600;
  }
  .statusbar .icons{display:flex; align-items:center; gap:5px}
  .sig{display:flex; align-items:flex-end; gap:2px; height:11px}
  .sig span{width:3px; background:#fff; border-radius:1px}
  .sig span:nth-child(1){height:4px} .sig span:nth-child(2){height:6px}
  .sig span:nth-child(3){height:8px} .sig span:nth-child(4){height:11px}
  .batt{width:24px;height:12px;border:1.3px solid #fff;border-radius:3.5px;position:relative;padding:1.5px}
  .batt::after{content:"";position:absolute;right:-4px;top:3.5px;width:2.5px;height:5px;background:#fff;border-radius:0 2px 2px 0}
  .batt i{display:block;height:100%;width:80%;background:#fff;border-radius:1.5px}

  .app{position:absolute; inset:0; padding-top:52px}
  .screen{
    position:absolute; inset:0; padding-top:52px; padding-bottom:86px; overflow-y:auto;
    opacity:0; pointer-events:none; transform:translateY(6px);
    transition:opacity .28s ease, transform .28s ease;
  }
  .screen.active{opacity:1; pointer-events:auto; transform:translateY(0)}
  .screen::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none}

  /* ================= Tab bar ================= */
  .tabbar{
    position:absolute; left:0; right:0; bottom:0; height:86px; padding-bottom:22px;
    background:rgba(15,17,19,0.86); backdrop-filter:blur(20px); border-top:1px solid var(--hair);
    display:flex; z-index:30;
  }
  .tab{flex:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:4px; background:none; border:none; color:var(--text-faint)}
  .tab svg{width:22px;height:22px; stroke:var(--text-faint); fill:none; stroke-width:1.7}
  .tab span{font-size:10.5px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:.01em}
  .tab.active{color:var(--text)}
  .tab.active svg{stroke:var(--calm-b)}

  /* ================= Shared bits ================= */
  .px{padding-left:22px; padding-right:22px}
  .eyebrow{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:.14em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--text-faint)}
  .h1{font-size:26px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.01em; margin-top:4px}
  .headrow{display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-start; margin-bottom:22px}
  .iconbtn{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--hair);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
  .iconbtn svg{width:16px;height:16px;stroke:var(--text-soft);fill:none;stroke-width:1.8}

  .card{background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--hair); border-radius:18px}

  /* ---- Today: hero state module ---- */
  .hero{padding:22px; text-align:center; position:relative; overflow:hidden; margin-bottom:16px}
  .hero-glow{position:absolute; inset:0; opacity:.5; pointer-events:none}
  .orb-wrap{width:180px;height:180px;margin:2px auto 6px; position:relative}
  .orb-wrap canvas{width:100%;height:100%;display:block}
  .detected{font-size:11px; color:var(--text-faint); margin-bottom:2px}
  .state-name{font-size:24px; font-weight:700}
  .state-sub{font-size:12.5px; color:var(--text-soft); margin-top:2px; margin-bottom:16px}
  .metrics-row{display:flex; gap:8px; margin-bottom:16px}
  .metric-chip{flex:1; background:var(--bg); border:1px solid var(--hair); border-radius:12px; padding:9px 4px}
  .metric-chip .l{font-size:9px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.05em; color:var(--text-faint); font-weight:600}
  .metric-chip .v{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:15px; font-weight:500; margin-top:2px}
  .cta{
    width:100%; padding:14px; border-radius:14px; border:none; font-size:14.5px; font-weight:700;
    color:#08110D; letter-spacing:.01em;
  }
  .haptic-note{display:flex; align-items:center; gap:7px; justify-content:center; font-size:11.5px; color:var(--text-faint); margin-top:12px}
  .haptic-dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%}

  /* ---- Today: timeline ---- */
  .section-title{font-size:13px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:10px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center}
  .section-title span.link{font-size:11.5px; color:var(--text-faint); font-weight:500}
  .timeline-card{padding:16px; margin-bottom:16px}
  .timeline-bar{display:flex; gap:2px; height:34px; border-radius:8px; overflow:hidden; margin-bottom:8px}
  .timeline-bar div{flex:1}
  .timeline-labels{display:flex; justify-content:space-between; font-size:9.5px; color:var(--text-faint); font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}
  .legend{display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; margin-top:12px}
  .legend .item{display:flex; align-items:center; gap:5px; font-size:10px; color:var(--text-soft)}
  .legend .dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%}

  .insight-preview{padding:16px; display:flex; gap:12px; align-items:flex-start; margin-bottom:8px}
  .insight-preview .ic{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--burnout-bg);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}
  .insight-preview .ic svg{width:17px;height:17px;stroke:var(--burnout-b);fill:none;stroke-width:1.7}
  .insight-preview .t{font-size:12.5px; font-weight:600}
  .insight-preview .d{font-size:11.5px; color:var(--text-soft); line-height:1.5; margin-top:2px}

  /* ---- Stages screen ---- */
  .stage-scroll{display:flex; gap:14px; overflow-x:auto; padding:0 22px 6px; scroll-snap-type:x mandatory}
  .stage-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none}
  .stage-card{
    scroll-snap-align:center; flex:0 0 278px; border-radius:22px; padding:20px;
    border:1px solid var(--hair); position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  }
  .stage-card .num{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.08em; margin-bottom:2px}
  .stage-card .name{font-size:20px; font-weight:700}
  .stage-card .sub{font-size:11.5px; color:var(--text-soft); margin-bottom:10px}
  .stage-card .mini-orb{width:110px;height:110px;margin:4px auto 10px}
  .stage-card .mini-orb canvas{width:100%;height:100%;display:block}
  .grammar-grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:7px; margin-bottom:12px}
  .grammar-item{background:rgba(0,0,0,0.24); border-radius:10px; padding:8px 9px}
  .grammar-item .gl{font-size:8.5px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.05em; opacity:.65; font-weight:600}
  .grammar-item .gv{font-size:11px; font-weight:600; margin-top:2px; line-height:1.3}
  .stage-haptic{display:flex; align-items:center; gap:7px; font-size:10.5px; padding-top:11px; border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)}
  .dotpager{display:flex; justify-content:center; gap:6px; margin:14px 0 4px}
  .dotpager span{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--hair)}
  .dotpager span.on{background:var(--text)}
  .thresh-table{width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:10.5px; margin-top:4px}
  .thresh-table th{text-align:left; padding:7px 8px; font-size:9px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.04em; color:var(--text-faint); font-weight:600; border-bottom:1px solid var(--hair)}
  .thresh-table td{padding:7px 8px; color:var(--text-soft); border-bottom:1px solid var(--hair)}
  .thresh-table tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none}

  /* ---- Insights screen ---- */
  .week-card{padding:18px; margin-bottom:16px}
  .week-bars{display:flex; align-items:flex-end; gap:8px; height:100px; margin:14px 0 8px}
  .week-bars .bcol{flex:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:6px; height:100%; justify-content:flex-end}
  .week-bars .bfill{width:100%; border-radius:5px 5px 3px 3px; min-height:6px}
  .week-bars .blabel{font-size:9px; color:var(--text-faint); font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}
  .burnout-card{padding:18px; border-color:rgba(156,148,238,0.35); background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(156,148,238,0.09), var(--surface) 60%)}
  .burnout-card .tag{display:inline-block; font-size:9.5px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.06em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--burnout-b); background:rgba(156,148,238,0.12); padding:4px 9px; border-radius:20px; margin-bottom:10px}
  .burnout-card h3{font-size:16px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:6px}
  .burnout-card p{font-size:12.5px; color:var(--text-soft); line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:12px}
  .reco{display:flex; gap:10px; padding:11px; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.22); border-radius:12px; margin-bottom:8px}
  .reco .rn{width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(156,148,238,0.18);color:var(--burnout-b);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}
  .reco .rt{font-size:11.5px; font-weight:600}
  .reco .rd{font-size:11px; color:var(--text-faint); margin-top:1px; line-height:1.4}
  .stat-row{display:flex; gap:10px; margin-bottom:16px}
  .stat-card{flex:1; padding:14px}
  .stat-card .l{font-size:9.5px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.05em; color:var(--text-faint); font-weight:600}
  .stat-card .v{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:19px; font-weight:600; margin-top:4px}
  .stat-card .trend{font-size:10.5px; margin-top:2px}

  /* ================= Projection (regulation) sheet ================= */
  .sheet{
    position:absolute; inset:0; background:#050607; z-index:60; border-radius:40px;
    transform:translateY(100%); transition:transform .4s cubic-bezier(.2,.9,.25,1);
    display:flex; flex-direction:column;
  }
  .sheet.open{transform:translateY(0)}
  .sheet-top{display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; padding:60px 20px 6px}
  .sheet-top .back{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;color:var(--text-soft);font-size:13px;font-weight:600;background:none;border:none}
  .sheet-top .back svg{width:16px;height:16px;stroke:var(--text-soft);fill:none;stroke-width:2}
  .sheet-title{font-size:12px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.04em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--text-faint)}

  .sheet-body{flex:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; padding:10px 24px 0; overflow-y:auto}
  .stage-pills{display:flex; gap:6px; margin:8px 0 18px}
  .stage-pill{padding:7px 14px; border-radius:20px; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; border:1px solid var(--hair); background:var(--surface); color:var(--text-soft)}
  .stage-pill.active{color:#fff}

  .proj-orb{width:250px;height:250px; margin:4px 0 4px; position:relative}
  .proj-orb canvas{width:100%;height:100%;display:block}
  .phase-pill{font-size:12px; font-weight:600; padding:6px 16px; border-radius:20px; margin:10px 0 4px; transition:all .3s}
  .breath-cue{font-size:15px; font-weight:600; min-height:26px; margin-bottom:6px; transition:transform .3s}
  .breath-cue.in{transform:scale(1.08)}
  .proj-timeline{width:100%; height:5px; background:var(--surface); border-radius:3px; overflow:hidden; margin:8px 0 18px}
  .proj-timeline-fill{height:100%; width:0%; transition:width .1s linear}

  .live-metrics{display:flex; gap:8px; width:100%; margin-bottom:16px}
  .live-metrics .m{flex:1; background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--hair); border-radius:12px; padding:10px 4px; text-align:center}
  .live-metrics .m .l{font-size:9px; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--text-faint); font-weight:600; letter-spacing:.04em}
  .live-metrics .m .v{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:14px; font-weight:600; margin-top:2px}

  .phase-card{width:100%; padding:14px; margin-bottom:14px}
  .phase-card .pt{font-size:12.5px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:5px}
  .phase-card .pd{font-size:12px; color:var(--text-soft); line-height:1.55}

  .sheet-controls{display:flex; gap:10px; padding:16px 24px 34px}
  .play-btn{flex:1; padding:15px; border-radius:14px; border:none; font-size:14.5px; font-weight:700; color:#08110D}
  .reset-btn{padding:15px 18px; border-radius:14px; border:1px solid var(--hair); background:var(--surface); color:var(--text-soft); font-size:13px; font-weight:600}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="device">
  <div class="screen-clip">
    <div class="statusbar">
      <span>9:41</span>
      <div class="icons">
        <div class="sig"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
        <div class="batt"><i></i></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="island"></div>

    <div class="app">

      <!-- ============ TODAY ============ -->
      <div class="screen active" id="screen-today">
        <div class="px">
          <div class="headrow">
            <div><div class="eyebrow">Tuesday, 2:26 PM</div><div class="h1">Today</div></div>
            <button class="iconbtn" aria-label="Settings"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.4 15a1.7 1.7 0 0 0 .34 1.87l.06.06a2 2 0 1 1-2.83 2.83l-.06-.06a1.7 1.7 0 0 0-1.87-.34 1.7 1.7 0 0 0-1 1.55V21a2 2 0 0 1-4 0v-.09A1.7 1.7 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.7 1.7 0 0 0-1.87.34l-.06.06a2 2 0 1 1-2.83-2.83l.06-.06A1.7 1.7 0 0 0 4.6 15a1.7 1.7 0 0 0-1.55-1H3a2 2 0 0 1 0-4h.09A1.7 1.7 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.7 1.7 0 0 0-.34-1.87l-.06-.06a2 2 0 1 1 2.83-2.83l.06.06A1.7 1.7 0 0 0 9 4.6a1.7 1.7 0 0 0 1-1.55V3a2 2 0 0 1 4 0v.09a1.7 1.7 0 0 0 1 1.55 1.7 1.7 0 0 0 1.87-.34l.06-.06a2 2 0 1 1 2.83 2.83l-.06.06A1.7 1.7 0 0 0 19.4 9a1.7 1.7 0 0 0 1.55 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 0 4h-.09a1.7 1.7 0 0 0-1.55 1z"/></svg></button>
          </div>

          <div class="card hero" id="hero-card">
            <div class="detected" id="hero-detected">DETECTED 12 MIN AGO</div>
            <div class="orb-wrap"><canvas id="hero-canvas" width="200" height="200"></canvas></div>
            <div class="state-name" id="hero-name">Strain</div>
            <div class="state-sub" id="hero-sub">Sustained activation — mental strain building</div>
            <div class="metrics-row">
              <div class="metric-chip"><div class="l">HRV</div><div class="v" id="hero-hrv">40 ms</div></div>
              <div class="metric-chip"><div class="l">Heart rate</div><div class="v" id="hero-hr">85 bpm</div></div>
              <div class="metric-chip"><div class="l">GSR</div><div class="v" id="hero-gsr">3.6 µS</div></div>
            </div>
            <button class="cta" id="open-regulation">Open regulation</button>
            <div class="haptic-note"><span class="haptic-dot" id="hero-hdot"></span><span id="hero-haptic">Double pulse felt at 2:14 PM</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="section-title">Today's pattern <span class="link">See stages ›</span></div>
          <div class="card timeline-card">
            <div class="timeline-bar" id="timeline-bar"></div>
            <div class="timeline-labels"><span>6AM</span><span>10AM</span><span>2PM</span><span>6PM</span><span>10PM</span></div>
            <div class="legend" id="timeline-legend"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="section-title">Pattern watch</div>
          <div class="card insight-preview">
            <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 1 0 10 10c0-1-.2-2-.5-3"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg></div>
            <div><div class="t">Strain has repeated 4 days this week</div><div class="d">Worth a look before it compounds — see Insights for the weekly view.</div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ============ STAGES ============ -->
      <div class="screen" id="screen-stages">
        <div class="px">
          <div class="eyebrow">Stress progression model</div>
          <div class="h1" style="margin-bottom:6px">Calm → Burnout</div>
          <div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--text-soft);line-height:1.55;margin-bottom:18px">One continuum, not five separate emotions — each stage is a threshold of accumulating physiological load. Swipe through to see how the projection changes at every level.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stage-scroll" id="stage-scroll"></div>
        <div class="dotpager" id="stage-dots"></div>
        <div class="px" style="margin-top:8px">
          <div class="section-title">Thresholds across all stages</div>
          <div class="card" style="padding:14px 6px">
            <table class="thresh-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Stage</th><th>HRV</th><th>HR</th><th>Duration</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody id="thresh-body"></tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div style="height:8px"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ============ INSIGHTS ============ -->
      <div class="screen" id="screen-insights">
        <div class="px">
          <div class="eyebrow">Weekly pattern</div>
          <div class="h1" style="margin-bottom:18px">Insights</div>

          <div class="stat-row">
            <div class="card stat-card"><div class="l">Avg HRV</div><div class="v">38 ms</div><div class="trend" style="color:var(--overload-b)">↓ 9% vs last week</div></div>
            <div class="card stat-card"><div class="l">Calm time</div><div class="v">2.1 hrs</div><div class="trend" style="color:var(--overload-b)">↓ 34% vs last week</div></div>
          </div>

          <div class="card week-card">
            <div class="section-title" style="margin-bottom:0">Daily baseline load</div>
            <div class="week-bars" id="week-bars"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="card burnout-card">
            <span class="tag">Pattern detected · not a single moment</span>
            <h3>Your baseline has been low for 9 days</h3>
            <p>This isn't a spike — HRV has stayed chronically flattened and GSR has stayed low across more than a week. PULSE treats this differently from acute overload: no urgent alert, no breathing prompt. The right response here is rest, not regulation.</p>
            <div class="reco"><div class="rn">1</div><div><div class="rt">Sustained rest, not a breathing exercise</div><div class="rd">In-the-moment techniques treat acute stress — they won't move a multi-day pattern.</div></div></div>
            <div class="reco"><div class="rn">2</div><div><div class="rt">Consider boundary-setting this week</div><div class="rd">Look at what's repeating across the days that scored highest.</div></div></div>
            <div class="reco"><div class="rn">3</div><div><div class="rt">Talk to someone if this continues</div><div class="rd">Professional support is appropriate once a pattern spans weeks, not days.</div></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- ============ TAB BAR ============ -->
    <div class="tabbar">
      <button class="tab active" data-screen="today"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 12h4l2-7 4 14 2-7h6"/></svg><span>Today</span></button>
      <button class="tab" data-screen="stages"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4.5"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1"/></svg><span>Stages</span></button>
      <button class="tab" data-screen="insights"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4 20V10M11 20V4M18 20v-7"/></svg><span>Insights</span></button>
    </div>

    <!-- ============ PROJECTION SHEET ============ -->
    <div class="sheet" id="sheet">
      <div class="sheet-top">
        <button class="back" id="sheet-back"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M15 18l-6-6 6-6"/></svg>Today</button>
        <div class="sheet-title">Regulation</div>
        <div style="width:52px"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="sheet-body">
        <div class="stage-pills" id="sheet-pills"></div>
